<i>adverb</i>: 번들번들 [번들번들], 반들반들 [반들반들] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>번들번들 [번들번들]</dt><br>
<dd>1. glossily; greasily</dd><br>
<dd>잘 닦고 기름칠을 한 듯 표면이 아주 매끄럽고 윤이 나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which the surface of something is very smooth as if it were polished and greased.</dd><br>
<dd>2. shrewdly; smartly</dd><br>
<dd>어리석은 데가 조금도 없이 꾀를 부리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being crafty, not stupid at all.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>반들반들 [반들반들]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lustrously; glossily; shiningly</dd><br>
<dd>빛이 날 만큼 겉이 아주 매끄럽고 윤이 나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which the surface of something is so smooth and glossy as to look shiny.</dd><br>
<dd>2. shrewdly; smartly</dd><br>
<dd>어수룩한 데 없이 약삭빠르거나 꾀를 부리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being shrewd or tricky, not stupid.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>